race.description: Breakout River Meats Cowra Cup Handicap
race.comment: FOX APPEAL (3) thrown in the deep end when a battling eighth over 1600m at Flemington. Earlier efforts were sound and he gets the right map favours today. Hard to stop. BLAZING GURU (13) progressed nicely second-up when she shouldered the 61.5kg for a gritty second over 1620m at Donald. Lightly raced mare with upside and the blinkers come off and the lugging bit goes on. Leading player. XCEPTIONAL FELLA (14) blinkers come off, and the winkers go on after he gripped on late to run fourth over 1650m at Moruya. Worthy contender from the draw. SHADOW DANE (8) holding his form and stays in the mix with the weight relief with Stiff's claim. Each way.
